    FeastPod -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Token/SSH"| Git
    FeastPod -->|"TLS<br/>Secret credentials"| Database
    FeastPod -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS creds"| S3

